                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout>
                           <p>Columns: 2;
                                                  ruled lines: 19;
                                                  written lines: 19; Uniform layout. Ruled with mastara. All books except Leviticus begin a new column.The beginning of a section marked in the margin by an ornamental pen and ink design, with פ in the centre.Each pericope divided into 7 sections numbered with Hebrew letters in the margin.The masorah magna in 1-3 lines in the upper and 2-7 lines in the lower margin.</p>
                        </layout>
                     </layoutDesc>
